__data__.text: Cont

Feature Intro

- Enhanced Security: Prevents unintended sharing of confidential data during screen sharing or calls.
- Unified Experience: Works across both SIM and VoIP calls initiated from the app.
- Compliance Ready: Aligns with organizational security and privacy policies.

On 25th November, the requirement was modified to accommodate a new action button 'Agree & Close' that has been added.

When the user clicks on this button, single/multi-factor authentication should be mandated.

Additionally, their explicit consent should be configured in the DB table for future reference and audit purposes.

8. logs the event

19. loop [Repeat these steps until failure is encountered or all the applicable challenge mechanisms are covered]
20. performs necessary steps for this scenario
21. returns the status of operation
22. user is navigated to the step up screen
23. user completes the step up
24. calls an API to verify eusenp or sep u
25. returns the status of operation
